import { Grid } from '@mantine/core'
import React from 'react'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Grid>
        <Grid.Col span={4}>
        1
      </Grid.Col>
      <Grid.Col span={4}>
        2
      </Grid.Col>
      <Grid.Col span={4}>
        3
      </Grid.Col>
    </Grid>
  )
}

export default Navbar
